00:43:22,361 --> 00:43:27,960
Don't feel bad about it when he trips over it, because they're just objects.

379
00:43:28,681 --> 00:43:30,841
These really, really bad people.

380
00:43:33,000 --> 00:43:37,881
They're the ultimately unresponsive people, unopened.

381
00:43:38,201 --> 00:43:44,041
They refuse all connections to stay self-sufficient.

